data.description: Welcome to 1949 Breck Ave! Move in ready, 4 bed 2.5 baths in desired Woodbridge Pointe! Hardwood floors throughout foyer, formal living and dining room. This home boasts an open floor plan along with all new appliances, hardware & kitchen backsplash in late 2020. Spacious bedrooms all located on second floor with 2 full bathrooms. Two zone HVAC, fully fenced backyard & ample parking / driveway space. Ask agent today about assumable VA loan at 3.125%
